WEBVTT

00:00.480 --> 00:01.800
Summer of the 24th year of Yuankang

00:01.800 --> 00:03.560
Prince of Jin captured Dongming

00:03.560 --> 00:04.920
Defeated the imperial army

00:05.320 --> 00:06.920
News reached the capital

00:06.920 --> 00:08.520
Officials were shocked

00:08.520 --> 00:10.120
The court was shaken

00:14.800 --> 00:16.120
The people are most important

00:16.120 --> 00:17.880
The state comes second

00:18.160 --> 00:19.600
The ruler is least

00:20.240 --> 00:20.840
Princess Consort

00:22.360 --> 00:23.080
Princess Consort

00:23.240 --> 00:24.160
When I went out just now

00:24.280 --> 00:25.200
I heard news

00:25.360 --> 00:27.160
His Highness has taken Dongming

00:30.240 --> 00:30.800
Mother

00:30.800 --> 00:32.680
Is Father coming back to get us?

00:35.920 --> 00:36.560
Yes

00:36.760 --> 00:38.120
Father is coming back

00:38.800 --> 00:40.480
What did Mother teach you before?

00:40.800 --> 00:42.280
Listen to Father

00:43.280 --> 00:44.440
Father has great things to do

00:44.600 --> 00:45.920
Don't cause Father trouble

00:47.880 --> 00:49.240
Sheng'er is good

01:05.280 --> 01:07.760
Today I come on behalf of His Majesty

01:07.960 --> 01:08.800
This

01:08.800 --> 01:10.800
Is an edict personally written by His Majesty

01:10.840 --> 01:13.280
The edict speaks of two things

01:13.800 --> 01:14.400
First

01:14.680 --> 01:16.840
The treacherous chancellor Chen Dao has corrupted the court

01:17.120 --> 01:19.800
His Majesty now understands the truth

01:20.240 --> 01:21.800
Wishes to remove the treacherous chancellor

01:22.280 --> 01:23.840
And execute the corrupt officials

01:25.200 --> 01:25.800
Second

01:25.880 --> 01:27.160
His Majesty deeply understands

01:27.240 --> 01:28.680
All of you present today

01:28.800 --> 01:30.720
Are all heroes of the northern expedition

01:30.800 --> 01:32.360
Not rebels

01:32.760 --> 01:34.120
His Majesty will not only not punish

01:34.120 --> 01:35.720
But will heavily reward you all

01:35.800 --> 01:37.960
Hopes you will do your utmost

01:37.960 --> 01:40.600
To recover the homeland soon

01:40.800 --> 01:42.240
The court will reward us

01:42.920 --> 01:44.280
The court will reward us

01:44.320 --> 01:45.280
The court will reward us

01:45.680 --> 01:46.160
Wonderful

01:46.680 --> 01:47.160
Wonderful

01:50.480 --> 01:53.280
His Majesty also has words for me to bring to Your Highness

01:55.120 --> 01:57.960
A family has come to this state

01:58.280 --> 01:59.920
What kind of situation is this?

02:04.240 --> 02:05.280
Tell the second son

02:06.280 --> 02:07.800
To withdraw to the north

02:08.000 --> 02:09.480
Send his family

02:10.400 --> 02:12.320
All to him

02:13.840 --> 02:14.920
This life

02:15.160 --> 02:16.360
Can't be lived together

02:17.280 --> 02:18.800
Then live apart

02:18.960 --> 02:20.360
After crossing the river

02:20.920 --> 02:22.080
He may raise

02:22.760 --> 02:24.440
The imperial banner

02:26.080 --> 02:27.680
North of Tianhe

02:29.120 --> 02:31.160
All will be under his rule

02:36.240 --> 02:37.120
Your Highness

02:37.560 --> 02:38.840
Accept the edict
